hopobject.name: Page
hopobject.body: Stolen credit card biscot pharmacy ltd “What appealed to me about it was how old fashioned it was, and I don’t mean that in a negative way, I mean it in a very positive way because I think from time to time we all yearn for those old movies which were all about character and about story. And I think that ‘Last Passenger’ had that. It reminded me of a Hitchcock thriller where Hitchcock used to invest in the characters, so whatever happened in the story, you really cared about them because he’d spent the time for you, the audience, to get to know them,” said Scottish actor Dougray Scott, who stars in the movie.
